query:
-- Add Efi (get the owner's ID for invitedBy)
INSERT INTO trip_collaborators (tripId, userId, permission, invitedBy, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 1, u.id, 'view_only', t.userId, NOW(), NOW()
FROM users u, trips t
WHERE u.email = 'gorene75@gmail.com' 
  AND u.openId NOT LIKE 'test-%'
  AND t.id = 1
LIMIT 1;
